'''Chief Representative Officer''' was the title of the leader of the [[Duros High House]], and thus of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. At the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Hoolidan Keggle]] was the CRO.

